dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
5 bar scales on map given in "Milliar germanic", "Leucae gallicae", "Milliar arabica", "Milliar turcica", and "Itinera sabbati".
Shows topography, drainage, territorial boundaries of the tribes of Israel, travel routes, places of historical interest.
2 decorative cartouches, with descriptive text and illustrations of men and a settlement.
Inset map: Regiunculae, in quas Palaestina olim fuit divisa delineatae.
